<Class name="CM_GapController" id="7172009e-ac00-41c3-9f34-991da8235267">
    <superclass name="CM_GridController"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Looks after the gaps between containers. Its TrackedItem list are those TIs that are connected to one of the gaps resources - power, water etc.
For Fork Lift Stacks this wil be used to specify a PowerTower and whether a gap is displayed in the Yard Display.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="location"/>
